plot: In the epic series finale, Supergirl is joined by familiar faces from the past to help her stop Lex and Nyxly for good. Meanwhile, Alex and Kelly prepare to walk down the aisle.

Supergirl must restore humanity to humanity when Lex and Nxyly steal it to power their battle against each with the pieces of the Allstsone. Afterward, Alex and Kelly get married, and some old friends attend the wedding. Kara gets some advice and a job offer from Cat Grant.—Gislef
